<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE LORD IS MY SHEPHERD</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa chu ei chingpa ahi,
 Tasam ngei hiel puong ka;
 Ham hing mun ah ei kuol saka,
 Chawlhna lui ah ei pui.

[V2]
 2. Ka hinna ei siemphat sak zel,
 Ama'n ei pui huoi-zel;
 Diktatna lampi ah ei pui,
 Amin lopi zalin.

[V3]
 3. Thihna lim guom hawh mahleng le,
 Thil phalo lau puong ka;
 Nei umpih a, na mawlh leh-
 Khetbuk in nei thamuon sek.

[V4]
 4. Ei dote muh in ka ma ah,
 Dawhkhang nei guon saka;
 Ka luchang thau na nuh ta a,
 Ka khawn a dim let hi.

[V5]
 5. Na phatna leh zangaihna chun,
 Ka damsung ei zui ding;
 Khutichun Lalpa In achun,
 Kumkhuo'n cheng zing tang ka.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>151</hymn_number>
</song>